cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI 

The paper proposes a pipeline for vehicle detection in aerial videos using deep learning and spatio-temporal filtering. This involves computer vision (cs.CV) techniques for object detection and tracking, robotics (cs.RO) for UAV or drone platforms, machine learning (cs.LG) for deep learning, multimedia (cs.MM) for video analytics, and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for intelligent fusion of multiple cues. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.MM, and cs.AI.
